<p>which shows the closeness to the Binomial<code class=3D"reqn"><span clas=
s=3D"katex"><span class=3D"katex-mathml"><math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1=
998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy=3D"false">(</mo><mi>k</mi><m=
o separator=3D"true">,</mo><mi>p</mi><mo stretchy=3D"false">)</mo></mrow><a=
nnotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">(k,p)</annotation></semantics></ma=
th></span><span class=3D"katex-html" aria-hidden=3D"true"><span class=3D"ba=
